dcterms:description: The TCGA dataset consists of gene expression measurements for cancer patients. There are 9659 samples for which we used the measurements from the 4000 most variable genes. The gene expression data was log-normalized and each feature was scaled in the [0, 1] interval.
dcterms:title: TCGA

dcterms:description: The News dataset consists of word counts for news items. We extracted 10000 news items each with 2858 features. The outcome can be thought of as user satisfaction.

dcterms:description: The MIMIC III database consists of observational data from patients in the ICU. We extracted 3000 patients that receive antibiotics treatment and used 9 clinical covariates as features.
